description:
Now to take you on the journey of the Mayflower ship. In 1602, this ship sailed from England to America and changed history forever. 130 passengers were fleeing persecution, and seeked for a place where they could worship freely. The Pilgrims made the journey from the land they knew into the unknown, thus leaving behind them a monumental legacy. 

To find out more information more information about the Mayflower read our extended article on our website. 
http://www.lineagejourney.com/episodes/episode-42-mayflower/
